Website: http://denovoassembler.sf.net

Ray is a parallel de novo genome assembler that utilise the message-passing interface everywhere.
Ray is implemented using peer-to-peer communication with the message-passing interface.
See http://www.parawiki.org/index.php/Message_Passing_Interface#Peer_to_Peer_Communication


Mailing list: denovoassembler-users <AT> lists.sourceforge.net


Installation


	tar xjf Ray-x.y.z.tar.bz2
	cd Ray-x.y.z
	make
	ls code/Ray


To run Ray on paired reads:

	mpirun -np 25 Ray -p lib1left.fasta lib1right.fasta -p lib2left.fasta lib2right.fasta -o prefix
	ls prefix.Contigs.fasta
	ls prefix.Scaffolds.fasta
	ls prefix.*



Code repository

	https://github.com/sebhtml/ray
